    "analysis": "From the prior aggregation step we computed global statistics (including p95) for component-KPI groups (agg_stats and agg_stats_top50). We also have a compact list of unique cmdb_id values across files, the top trace_name and kpi_name frequencies, and discovered no log_name entries in log.csv. This gives us global thresholds required before filtering for the incident window. Next we must detect metric anomalies inside the incident window (March 4, 2021 21:00 to 21:30 UTC+8) using those global thresholds to narrow candidate faulty component-KPIs. Logs appear empty so metrics and traces will be the primary sources for localization.",
